-- Ex-Morgan Crucible CEO Didn't Order Files Shredded, Witness Says at Trial
-- Jef Feeley
-- 2010-07-14T20:03:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/ex-morgan-crucible-ceo-didn-t-order-files-shredded-witness-says-at-trial.html

          
          
             Ex-Morgan Crucible Co. Chief
Executive Officer Ian Norris didn’t’ order the destruction of
documents about price-fixing meetings with competitors, a former
executive of the ceramics maker testified in Norris’s criminal
trial.  
